OL,3,CSuper soil: How a farmer makes money
OL,4,Cfrom storing carbon underground
OL,6,FA farmer in Leicestershire who became
OL,7,Fthe first in the UK to sell off
OL,8,Fcredits from the carbon in his soil,
OL,9,Fsays time is running out for British
OL,10,Fagriculture to take action against
OL,11,Fclimate change.
OL,13,FHylton Murray-Philipson, who runs
OL,14,FBlaston Farm near Market Harborough,
OL,15,Fswitched to regenerative farming
OL,16,Fmethods around eight years ago, after
OL,17,Fnoticing the heavily-farmed soil on
OL,18,Fhis land was "lifeless".
