OL,3,CSuper soil: How a farmer makes money
OL,4,Cfrom storing carbon underground
OL,6,FSince then, he has been able to
OL,7,Frejuvenate his soil so that it stores
OL,8,Fhigh amounts of carbon, which is
OL,9,Fmeasured and sold as "carbon credits"
OL,10,Fto companies looking to offset their
OL,11,Fimpact.
OL,13,FHylton said: "For 50 years, almost no
OL,14,Ffarmers put soil at the centre of
OL,15,Ftheir thinking, and took it for
OL,16,Fgranted.
OL,18,F"You really need to look after your
OL,19,Fsoil, and if you do that, the soil
OL,20,Fwill look after you."
