OL,3,CSuper soil: How a farmer makes money
OL,4,Cfrom storing carbon underground
OL,6,FAfter decades of constant, traditional
OL,7,Ffarming methods on Blaston Farm,
OL,8,FHylton noticed the soil was barren and
OL,9,Fdry - and the farm even suffered flash
OL,10,Fflooding because of it.
OL,12,FHe said: "It was lifeless, it was
OL,13,Fabsolutely inert - rock solid. It had
OL,14,Fno life in it at all.
OL,16,F"But then we walked about 50 yards
OL,17,Finto a wood planted around 50 years
OL,18,Fago and it was a totally different
OL,19,Fstory.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
