OL,3,CSuper soil: How a farmer makes money
OL,4,Cfrom storing carbon underground
OL,6,F"The soil was full of life, there were
OL,7,Fworms everywhere. I just thought the
OL,8,Fcontrast was so extreme, we can't go
OL,9,Fon like that."
OL,11,FHylton made some big changes with a
OL,12,Ffocus on sustainability - from
OL,13,Fplanting hundreds of trees to
OL,14,Fintroducing a crop and livestock
OL,15,Frotation system, so as not to tire the
OL,16,Fsoil.
OL,18,FThe problem with bare soil
