OL,3,CSuper soil: How a farmer makes money
OL,4,Cfrom storing carbon underground
OL,6,FHylton said: "Basically this soil is
OL,7,Fnever bare, so at the moment you've
OL,8,Fgot both clover and barley.
OL,10,F"When I remove the barley after
OL,11,Fharvest, the clover is still there
OL,12,Fconverting sunlight into leaf matter
OL,13,Fand also feeding the roots.
OL,15,F"All the CO2 that we've been releasing
OL,16,Ffor the last 50 years is being put
OL,17,Fback into the soil, where it belongs."
