OL,3,CSuper soil: How a farmer makes money
OL,4,Cfrom storing carbon underground
OL,6,FHylton became the first farmer in the
OL,7,FUK to generate income from the amount
OL,8,Fof carbon he stores, by selling
OL,9,F"carbon credits" to businesses.
OL,11,FIt fit the sustainable ethos of the
OL,12,Fmen behind Dash Water - a drinks
OL,13,Fcompany taking wonky surplus fruit to
OL,14,Finfuse sparkling water. The business
OL,15,Fhas become one of many to offset their
OL,16,Fcarbon footprint by supporting and
OL,17,Finvesting in Blaston Farm.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
