OL,3,CSuper soil: How a farmer makes money
OL,4,Cfrom storing carbon underground
OL,6,FJack Scott, co-founder of Dash, said:
OL,7,F"For any business, we believe starting
OL,8,Fout in should be responsible and
OL,9,Fshould make as little impact as
OL,10,Fpossible on the environment they are
OL,11,Fin.
OL,13,F"We were so excited when we met
OL,14,FHylton. He really is at the forefront
OL,15,Fof regenerative farming, something we
OL,16,Fwholeheartedly support.
OL,18,F"We buy the credits off Hylton here at
OL,19,FBlaston, and we know exactly how much
OL,20,Fcarbon we are offsetting at Dash."
