OL,3,CSuper soil: How a farmer makes money
OL,4,Cfrom storing carbon underground
OL,6,FThanks to the investment from local
OL,7,Fbusinesses, Blaston Farm generates
OL,8,Fenough income to keep working on
OL,9,Fregeneration, rather than having the
OL,10,Fwhole farm under constant pressure to
OL,11,Fproduce profits from crops.
OL,13,FHealthy, fertile soil also means the
OL,14,Ffarm doesn't have to rely on chemicals
OL,15,Fand fertilisers for their food
OL,16,Fproduction, which have seen prices
OL,17,Fsoar after Brexit and the war in
OL,18,FUkraine.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
