OL,3,CSuper soil: How a farmer makes money
OL,4,Cfrom storing carbon underground
OL,6,FHylton says time is running out to
OL,7,Fstop climate change, and soil could be
OL,8,Fa quick solution if more farmers put
OL,9,Fit as their top priority.
OL,11,FHe said: "Soil has the ability to
OL,12,Fstore more carbon than the rainforests
OL,13,Fand the atmosphere combined.
OL,15,F"So, if we are going to hit our
OL,16,Ftargets of 2030, 2040, 2050, whatever
OL,17,Fit is - if we don't harness the power
OL,18,Fof soil on a global scale, then we are
OL,19,Fnot going to hit those targets."
